Explore BUSINESS















Increase Government Sales.
Effortlessly find new local, state and federal agency customers directly from their purchasing data.


Request Access 





 





It’s the purchase orders that tell the WHOLE story.



  

The U.S. government spends $7 trillion per year. Eighty percent of that spending does not go out for public bid. 80%! However, the one place that you can see all of the details of an agency’s spending is on their purchase orders. 
Purchase orders identify specific sellers, product and service descriptions, quantities, prices, discounts, payment terms, dates and other details. The power comes in bringing all of that information together in one database and making it easily searchable for government vendors. 
SmartProcure aggregates hundreds of millions of purchase orders from schools, local, state and federal agencies so that businesses that sell into the government can easily see who buys their products, how much they pay and who they purchase them from. Thousands of businesses and government sales managers use SmartProcure to effortlessly find new customers and use pricing intelligence to increase their government wins. 






  


SmartSearch

 Accelerate productivity and boost sales back in line with your goals. Call on the agencies that you know are purchasing the goods and services you sell and never again waste time fishing for competitor pricing. 







  



SmartExport

Integrate SmartProcure data directly into your CRM or back-end system. 
              SmartExport provides an Excel/CSV compatible file of detailed purchase order data from the local, state and federal government agencies that are providing data to the SmartProcure system.
 







  

"SmartProcure's data also allows businesses to search for the areas where their product is likely to be in highest demand."




  

"SmartProcure provides a wealth of valuable information for suppliers. Suppliers are willing to purchase the insights from procurement data."




  

"SmartProcure gives our users the ability to see precisely how to competitively price and market their products and services."




  

“[SmartProcure] operates as a searchable database of government procurement information, allowing users to find a whole range of past deals.”










Other businesses who are doing amazing things with SmartProcure:















